    <Section containerClass="max-w-4xl mx-auto pb-24">
      <article class="c-content prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>
          These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the CoClaw website at
          <strong>coclaw.com</strong> (the "Site"). By using the Site, you agree to these Terms.
